  "subject": "Chore: Modernize docs configuration for Python 3.12+",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Modernize docs configuration for Python 3.12+\n\nRemove broken/outdated Python modules that are incompatible with modern\nPython versions. Update .readthedocs.yaml to use ubuntu-24.04 and Python\n3.13. Modernize tox.ini (pin basepython to 3.12, use local constraints\ninstead of remote URLs). Add etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt from the doc\nrepo.\n\nUpdate JIRA URLs from jira.onap.org to lf-onap.atlassian.net to fix\nlinkcheck failures caused by the JIRA migration to Atlassian Cloud\n(the old domain redirects to an incorrect URL path that 404s).\n\nAdd wiki.onap.org to linkcheck_ignore as the Confluence wiki also\nmigrated to Atlassian Cloud and the old page IDs are not resolvable\nat the new location. Also fix invalid glob patterns in linkcheck_ignore\nto use proper regex syntax.\n\nRemoved modules: sphinxcontrib-swaggerdoc, six.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I2985d054e9d7eb90e783cf36720a94e19ebd3ade\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
